We also read about <a href="http://www.offworld.com/2008/12/the-cats-cradle-balance-of-str.html">the precarious rebalancing of <em>Street Fighter II</em></a> for its Xbox 360/PS3 remake (and re-watched the most thrilling <em>Street Fighter</em> championship video ever recorded), and watched <a href="http://www.offworld.com/2008/12/a-new-look-at-thatgamecompanys.html">new footage of Thatgamecompany's serene <em>Flower</em></a>, a game that flexes every bit of the PS3's muscle purely to render fluttering petals and waves of tall grass. 

